uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.data

Class NamedFilterWrapper<T extends DataObject>

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.model.data.NamedFilterWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - targe type of filters
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Contexed, NamedFilterProvider<T>

    public class NamedFilterWrapper<T extends DataObject>
extends java.lang.Object
implements NamedFilterProvider<T>, Contexed
    A wrapper for resolving named filters from a DataObjectFactory. The factory itself and its Composites are checked if they implement NamedFilterProvider A name of the form field_name->remote_name indicates a remote filter should be constructed via field field_name and the same algorithm applied on the remote factory. Only references registered in the Repository can be de-referenced.

    spb
